          "_name": "contacts02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"contacts02 map1\" group=\"Contact\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Title\" name=\"showCardTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        <header>Map</header>\n        <input type=\"map\" title=\"Map\" name=\"googleMap\" place-id=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps?q=Одеса,+вулиця+Богдана+Хмельницького,+62&amp;output=embed&amp;z=17&quot;width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\" value=\"<iframe src=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps?q=Одеса,+вулиця+Богдана+Хмельницького,+62&amp;output=embed&amp;z=17&quot;width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; style=&quot;border:0;&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer-when-downgrade&quot;></iframe>\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/605143641_1591118048549738_5747359174254957557_n-1280x960.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.2\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n                <div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n                    <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                        <b>Контакти</b>\n                    </h3>\n                    <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                        Contacts Subtitle\n                    </h4>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                        <h5 mbr-text class=\"cardTitle mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" data-app-selector=\".cardTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Зв'яжіться з нами</b></h5>\n                        <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".list, .item-wrap\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                            <li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">ЄДРПОУ 36503293\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">65005, м. Одеса, вул. Б. Хмельницького, 62</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">65007, м. Одеса, вул. Пантелеймонівська, 101</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><br></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">Тел./факс: <a href=\"tel:(048) 705 54 77\" class=\"text-primary\"></a><a href=\"tel:(048) 705 54 78\" class=\"text-primary\">(048) 705 54&nbsp;78</a></li>\n                            <li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">Е-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:tc.khadzhybeiskyi@dpsp.omr.gov.ua\" class=\"text-primary\">tc.khadzhybeiskyi@dpsp.omr.gov.ua</a></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><br></li>\n                            <li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\"><b>Режим роботи Територіального центру:\n</b></li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">понеділок – четвер – з 08:00 до 17:00\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">п’ятниця<b> </b>- з 08:00 до 15:45\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">субота, неділя – вихідний\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">обідня перерва – з 12:00 до 12:45</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">\n</li><li class=\"mbr-text item-wrap\">\n</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"map-wrapper col-md-12 col-lg-6\">\n                <div class=\"google-map\" mbr-map=\"googleMap\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
